\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {2}{\ignorespaces (a)~Schedule comparison: $\exp (\eta (1/u-1))$ (solid) vs.\ $u^{-\eta }$ (dashed) across the full urgency range. Red region: hard wall backstop active ($u < 0.05$). (b)~Relative approximation error. The schedules agree within 10\% for $u > 0.5$ (the regime where smooth pacing operates).}}{7}{figure.caption.4}\protected@file@percent }
